-- Asian Finance Bank CEO Says Capitalization Critical for Islamic Finance
-- B y
-- 2010-10-25T03:25:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/asian-finance-bank-ceo-says-capitalization-critical-for-islamic-finance.html
Mohamed Azahari Kamil, chief 
executive officer of Asian Finance Bank Bhd., the Kuala 
Lumpur-based unit of Qatar Islamic Bank SAQ, talks about the 
outlook for the Islamic finance industry and the company's 
business strategy.  Azahari speaks in Kuala Lumpur with Haslinda Amin on 
Bloomberg Television's "On the Move Asia." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 02:19